;HIS91 IS MONOPROTONATED ON THE EPSILON NITROGEN.
HIS40 IS DIPROTONATED.
HIS57 HAS A MONOPROTONATED COMPONENT (PROTON ON ND1),
COORDINATING ZN+2 THROUGH NE2, AND A DIPROTONATED COMPONENT.
THE DIPROTONATED COMPONENT MAKES A HYDROGEN-BONDED SALT
BRIDGE WITH SULFATE_467. THE COMPONENTS ARE UNRESOLVED.
